General_review: Kalha is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Breakfast, Arabic, Falafel that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Airport, Ali Sabah Al-Salem - Umm Al Hayman, Doha and Ghornata.
Their best selling dishes are (12) Pieces Falafel, Zahara Moshakil - Ma'aoon, Hommous and Kudsiya, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Breakfast, Arabic, Falafel.
They have been reviewed 61022 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.

General_review: Alternative is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Healthy, Desserts, Ice Cream that delivers across Jabriya, Sabah Al-Salem and Sharq.

Their best selling dishes are Al Shabah Air Baked Meal, Chicken Strips, Twister Wrap and Alternative Wrap , although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Healthy, Desserts, Ice Cream.

General_review: Police Steak is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Sandwiches, Burgers, Grills that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa and Abu Hasaniya.

Their best selling dishes are Chicken Fillet Meal, Individual Chicken Fillet Meal, Kids Meal Fillet and Spicy Chicken Fillet Meal, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Sandwiches, Burgers, Grills.
They have been reviewed 40596 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.

General_review: Mayar is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Grills, Lebanese, Breakfast that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa and Abu Hasaniya.
Their best selling dishes are Tabbouleh, Spicy Potato, Hummus With Tahini and Vine Leaves, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Grills, Lebanese, Breakfast.
They have been reviewed 10770 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.

General_review: Steak & Fahita Stations is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Sandwiches, Burgers, Shawarma that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa and Abu Hasaniya.

Their best selling dishes are Fajita Station Meal, Philadelphia, Chicken Fillet Meal and Chicken Twister, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Sandwiches, Burgers, Shawarma.
They have been reviewed 5759 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.

General_review: Nab3 Al Diyafa is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Breakfast, Pastries, Saj that delivers across Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa, Abu Hasaniya and Adailiya.

Their best selling dishes are Potato Chips, Chicken Fillet (Meal), Chicken Fillet (Sandwich) and Tasty (Meal), although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Breakfast, Pastries, Saj.
They have been reviewed 1939 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.

They have been reviewed 1525 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.
